			</div>
			
			<div class="app-text-container">
			<p class="app-text">ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE</p
			</div>
			
			<p class="app0-text">Artificial Intelligence (AI) is a branch of computer science that focuses on the creation of intelligent machines that can perform tasks that usually require 
			human intelligence, such as learning, problem-solving, and decision making. AI involves the development of algorithms, computer programs, and systems that can process data, recognize 
			patterns, and learn from experience. The applications of AI are vast and include natural language processing, image and speech recognition, robotics, autonomous vehicles, fraud detection, 
			recommendation systems, and personalized marketing. AI has the potential to revolutionize industries such as healthcare, finance, transportation, and manufacturing, by making processes 
			more efficient, reducing costs, and improving decision-making.</p>
			
			<div class="appcareers1-text-container">
			<img src="char.png" class="first-image"
			</div>
			
			<div class="app1-text-container">
			<p class="appp-text">CHARACTER MODELING</p
			</div>
			
			<p class="app1-text">Character modeling is the process of developing 3D models of characters for use in a variety of fields, including animation, film, and video games. The physical 
			characteristics of a character, such as their shape, texture, and color, are represented digitally using specialized software. Character modeling is a technique used in the video game 
			business to develop playable characters. Character modeling is a technique used in animation and film to give figures life and produce realistic animations.  Specialized artists with 
			training in traditional art and 3D modeling software frequently carry out this work.</p>
			
			<div class="appcareers2-text-container">
			<img src="vol.png" class="first-image"
			</div>
			
			<div class="app2-text-container">
			<p class="apppp-text">VOLUNTEER WORK</p
			</div>
			
			<p class="app2-text">Volunteering involves lending a hand with projects or chores involving technology for organizations, communities, or individuals. These initiatives can include 
			creating websites or software programs, offering technical support, or imparting technology knowledge to others. Volunteering in the field of technology can have a big impact on society. 
			For instance, technology volunteers can assist nonprofit organizations with the development of social media campaigns, databases, and website creation and maintenance. Additionally, 
			they can collaborate with educational institutions or community organizations to train marginalized populations in technical skills so they are successful in the digital age.</p>
			
			<div class="appcareers3-text-container">
			<img src="open.png" class="first-image"
			</div>
			
			<div class="app3-text-container">
			<p class="appppp-text">OPEN-SOURCE PROJECTS</p
			</div>
			
			<p class="app3-text">Open source projects have numerous and various applications. To create websites, mobile applications, and desktop programs, many businesses, groups, and people use
			open source software. Open source initiatives have emerged as a crucial component of the technological ecosystem, powering everything from operating systems and machine learning frameworks
			to web browsers and database management systems. Developers can develop new skills, expand their portfolios, and work with other developers from across the world by contributing to open 
			source projects. Additionally, open source projects allow developers the chance to give back to the community by applying their knowledge and experience to initiatives that help others.</p>
			
			<div class="appcareers4-text-container">
			<img src="fifth.png" class="first-image"
			</div>
			
			<div class="app4-text-container">
			<p class="apppppp-text">HACKATHONS</p
			</div>
			
			<p class="app4-text">Hackathons give participants an opportunity to work with others who share their interests, pick up new skills, and maybe receive rewards or get employment. 
			Hackathons can also generate original solutions to difficult challenges and serve as a venue for networking and professional growth. Hackathons are occasions where individuals 
			gather to work together on technology projects in a condensed period of time, usually lasting from 24 to 48 hours. A hackathon's objective is to create a working prototype or fix 
			for a particular issue. Hackathon participants can have a variety of backgrounds, such as those in software development, design, marketing, and business.</p>
			
			<div class="appcareers5-text-container">
			<img src="last.png" class="first-image"
			</div>
			
			<div class="app5-text-container">
			<p class="appppppp-text">FREELANCING</p
			</div>
			
			<p class="app5-text">Working on temporary assignments for clients under a contract is referred to as freelancing. It's a versatile and well-liked way to use your technological expertise.
			There are many fields where freelance employment is available, such as web development, mobile app development, and digital marketing. You can select your own clients, set your own hours,
			and create a portfolio of work as a freelancer. Freelancing can be a fantastic method to advance your profession, build an audience, and get experience. Freelancing is used in many 
			different areas, including technology. Freelancers have the flexibility to work remotely, giving businesses access to an internation staffwithout worrying about boundaries imposed by 
			location.</p>
